description: Represents the success of a third party job as returned to the pipeline by a job worker. Used for partner actions only.

parameters.name: jobId
parameters.description: The ID of the job that successfully completed. This is the same ID returned from PollForThirdPartyJobs.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: The clientToken portion of the clientId and clientToken pair used to verify that the calling entity is allowed access to the job and its details.

parameters.name: currentRevision
parameters.description: Represents information about a current revision. The revision ID of the current version of an artifact. The change identifier for the current revision. created (datetime) --- The date and time when the most recent revision of the artifact was created, in timestamp format. revisionSummary (string) --- The summary of the most recent revision of the artifact.

nested_params.name: revision
nested_params.description: The revision ID of the current version of an artifact.

nested_params.name: changeIdentifier
nested_params.description: The change identifier for the current revision.

nested_params.name: created
nested_params.description: The date and time when the most recent revision of the artifact was created, in timestamp format.

nested_params.name: revisionSummary
nested_params.description: The summary of the most recent revision of the artifact.

parameters.name: executionDetails
parameters.description: The details of the actions taken and results produced on an artifact as it passes through stages in the pipeline. summary (string) --- The summary of the current status of the actions. externalExecutionId (string) --- The system-generated unique ID of this action used to identify this job worker in any external systems, such as CodeDeploy. percentComplete (integer) --- The percentage of work completed on the action, represented on a scale of 0 to 100 percent.

nested_params.name: summary
nested_params.description: The summary of the current status of the actions.

nested_params.name: externalExecutionId
nested_params.description: The system-generated unique ID of this action used to identify this job worker in any external systems, such as CodeDeploy.

nested_params.name: percentComplete
nested_params.description: The percentage of work completed on the action, represented on a scale of 0 to 100 percent.
